      <title>办公大楼重塑了美国的天际线。现在建筑起重机正在消失。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/commercial-real-estate-trouble-evident-in-fading-downtown-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当拉姆·伊曼纽尔（Rahm Emanuel）统治芝加哥并想夸耀这座城市的健康状况时，时任市长指出了天际线上的建筑起重机的数量—— 2017年底为60人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/commercial-real-estate-trouble-evident-in-fading-downtown-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 11:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非矿业产量第四季度反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/south-african-mining-production-recovers-in-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非矿业产量在去年最后三个月出现反弹，成为该行业的一个亮点，该行业 2023 年总体产量按年率计算有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/south-african-mining-production-recovers-in-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:16:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
